Hate 

I hate the way I talk, walk,
sit,stand.
I hate the way I can't cry when I want to.
I hate the way I can't meet people's expectations.
I hate the fact I'm so useless.
I hate the fact I can't talk to someone without 
stuttering. 
I hate the fact I feel disgusted everytime I look at 
myself in the mirror.
I hate my smile that fuels my anger and never my joy.
Hate is such a strong word.
If I hate something I hate it with all my heart
and soul.